---
title: Sweet-Soy Tofu, Beef & Greens Poke Bowl with Sesame Seeds & Pickled Cucumber
description: We love poke bowls because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This version uses marinated tofu, beef strips, Asian greens and cucumber, with a sprinkle of sesame seeds to tie the whole thing together.
